\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s1\sl276\slmult1\qj{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\sa200\rtlch\af3\afs22\lang1025\ltrch\dbch\af3\langfe255\hich\f3\fs22\lang1033\loch\f3\fs22\lang1033 {\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f3\fs22\lang1033\i0\b0 [4]\tab In terms of the proposed transaction Powertech\'92s plan is to purchase the entire issued share capital of IST Group provided that two of its divisions i.e. IST Dynamics and IST Nuclear are unbundled from IST Group.  In this way Powertech will control IST
 Group and its five remaining divisions.}
